eu.kartoffelquadrat.xoxinternals.service

Interface Action

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    XoxClaimFieldAction

    public interface Action
    Generic Action interface for blackboard architecture. Implement your own actions, representing kinds of actions performed by players in a blackboard architecture. Actions are generated by a custom ActionGenerator and performed by a custom ActionInterpreter.
    Author:
    Maximilian Schiedermeier
